episodes.name: A Fancy Article and a Scholarship for a Baby
episodes.overview: Sheldon's published paper leads to a frenzy of grad school recruiting, and Georgie tries to speak more properly in front of his daughter.

episodes.name: Community Service and the Key to a Happy Marriage
episodes.overview: Connie gets assigned a tough probation officer, and Georgie takes marriage advice from his father-in-law.

episodes.name: A Little Snip and Teaching Old Dogs
episodes.overview: George Sr. is worried that Mary wants another baby and gets a vasectomy behind her back. Meanwhile, Drs. Linkletter and Sturgis go to Sheldon for science tutoring.

episodes.name: A New Home and a Traditional Texas Torture
episodes.overview: George Sr. gets an exciting job offer, and Sheldon prepares for his move to California.

episodes.name: Funeral (1)
episodes.overview: Sheldon leaves East Texas for the California Institute of Technology following the death of his father, George Cooper Sr.

episodes.name: Memoir (2)
